This one asked me to bring him to you.
Approach!

317
00:18:33.875 --> 00:18:36.458
He has an urgent message for the emperor.

318
00:18:36.958 --> 00:18:37.916
Your Imperial Highness.

319
00:18:38.000 --> 00:18:38.958
[kisses]

320
