385
00:22:19.875 --> 00:22:22.666
â™ª <i>That broke the court with wicked din </i>â™ª

386
00:22:22.750 --> 00:22:26.250
â™ª <i>And since the queen had made no heirs </i>â™ª

387
00:22:26.333 --> 00:22:30.541
â™ª <i>A prince was born with curly hairs! </i>â™ª

388
00:22:30.625 --> 00:22:33.583
â™ª <i>"An heir's an heir." came from the pop </i>â™ª

389
00:22:33.666 --> 00:22:36.291
â™ª <i>"An heir's an heir"</i>
<i>That's from the top! </i>â™ª

390
00:22:36.375 --> 00:22:38.500
- â™ª <i>And that's the tale</i>â€¦ â™ª
- [Jaskier] â™ª <i>That's the tale </i>â™ª

391
00:22:38.583 --> 00:22:41.541
â™ª <i>That's the tale. that's the tale </i>â™ª

392
00:22:41.625 --> 00:22:47.291
[all harmonizing] â™ª <i>Of King Lambchop! </i>â™ª

