413
00:23:25.500 --> 00:23:28.708
It's bold of you to be marching
along the highway singing.

414
00:23:28.791 --> 00:23:31.208
I don't reckon weepin' as we go
would be any better.

415
00:23:31.291 --> 00:23:32.500
[Percival chuckles]

416
