- Magical scum!

464
00:25:22.583 --> 00:25:25.291
- [man 5] Kill her!
- The blood of this war is on your hands!

465
00:25:25.375 --> 00:25:27.750
Yen. get inside! Yen!

466
00:25:27.833 --> 00:25:30.041
- [woman 3] You witch!
- [woman 1] Fuck off. you traitor!

467
00:25:30.125 --> 00:25:32.250
